name: Pure BB Cream
description:
BB (Blemish Balm) Cream 

Daily all in one product. 

Evens skin tone, blurs imperfections, smoothes fine lines and hydrates the skin.

Contains Collagen, Allantoin, Avocado Oil, Aloe Vera, Mineral Pigments and Vitamin E. 

Available in 3 shades, Ultra Light, Light and Medium.

name: Pure Under Eye Roll On
description:
Stimulates tired skin and reduces the appearance of under eye bags. 

Enriched with Cucumber and Caffeine. 

Dermatologically and Ophthalmologically tested
